<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Sherwood</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A charming residential neighborhood located within the northwest quadrant of Calgary, Sherwood is bounded by the <a href="/nolan-hill.php">Nolan Hill</a> Community to the north, the Sarcee Trail to the west, the Shaganappi Trail to the east and the <a href="/hamptons.php">Hamptons</a> community to the south. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The award-winning community, Sherwood Real estate offers some of the most breathtaking views of the natural ravine system and the rolling countryside. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Sherwood include a variety of residential options from row houses, to single-family detached homes and apartment condos, with a typical unit being listed at an average price of $600,000.</p>
        </div>
